{"tid":2046550,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"整咗隻拖延撚專用嘅專注力計時app","createTime":"2020-06-01T13:07:40.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-01T16:18:21.000Z","uid":356648,"like":11,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"1049bc072f9064bc957e05f09b2820b21f1b3a73","tid":2046550,"uid":356648,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-01T13:07:40.000Z","msg":"隻app叫Refocus 主要功能係幫你輕輕鬆鬆咁做嘢 <span style=\"color: red;\">分咗心嘅時候提你專心返</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n點解人會拖延呢？<br />\n根據<span style=\"color: red;\">柏金遜定律 Parkinson&rsquo;s Law</span> 俾五日時間你去寫一篇只需要三日就完成到嘅文 你最尾都係要五日先寫得完<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/CmyUbrx.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCmyUbrx.png&h=98dcabf4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">解決拖延嘅最好方法就係制造迫切性</span> 隻app有兩個計時器一齊行緊 細鐘五分鐘就會響一次 大鐘係你自己訂嘅deadline<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/point1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/QVZDCXi.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQVZDCXi.png&h=f83642dc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n你可以set一個目標 例如11點之前想集中1個鐘<br />\n如果你嗰陣幾精神 個目標可以定高啲 重點係俾自己選擇<br />\n因為好多人覺得自己做嘢唔夠專心 就會迫自己做嘢 但係<span style=\"color: red;\">越迫就越唔想做嘢 變咗惡性循環</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1NShTvP.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1NShTvP.png&h=9e031435&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n另一個解決拖延方法就係<span style=\"color: red;\">利用群眾壓力</span> 你話俾全世界知你想集中幾耐 最尾再自爆自己完成到幾多個巴仙<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yeah.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n為咗唔想太樣衰你就自然會勤力少少<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n同埋有冇試過明明個心好想做嘢 但係就點都專注唔到？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n因為人有好多器官接收外界事物 身體入面都有好多sensor detect係咪肚餓 口喝呀 急尿呀咁 仲未計你個腦會無啦啦諗起啲嘢<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n即係話 <span style=\"color: red;\">根本人嘅設計就係唔可以專心咁連續做同一樣嘢好耐</span><br />\n<br />\n就算你熄咗部電話 走埋入個山洞入面都重係會有好多嘢distract緊你<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9Q1uKC4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9Q1uKC4.png&h=7984f30e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">隻app冇限你要連續做幾耐嘢</span> set咗目標之後就舒舒服服咁做 做到攰就抖下 做到興起就做耐啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n你做緊嘢嘅時候收到個WhatsApp都可以覆兩句 唔會影響計時 （某啲focus timer app會限住你搞到好大壓力）<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/NprKywS.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNprKywS.png&h=60da1798&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/fMOH4Dy.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FfMOH4Dy.png&h=d998a355&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n仲有圖表stat同日暦 幫你記低你幾時集中咗幾耐<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n今日啱啱完成咗第一個version 希望大家俾下意見 等我可以一路改進隻app<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"30a69b216d48fed881e2b0222090673279591595","tid":2046550,"uid":273627,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-01T13:10:16.000Z","msg":"唔想清deadline然後見到巴打個po<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"86449fe5aed27cfc71fa242685b60cc12577d82c","tid":2046550,"uid":356648,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"30a69b216d48fed881e2b0222090673279591595","tid":2046550,"uid":273627,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-01T13:10:16.000Z","msg":"唔想清deadline然後見到巴打個po<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-01T13:11:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"20b87f6ae15cfa35fa3e8c95343604ac851a1c25","tid":2046550,"uid":49004,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-01T13:11:42.000Z","msg":"都係等第日先download <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4f436fc1d4557d540facaec754a446c12d30d62d","tid":2046550,"uid":130698,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-01T13:13:21.000Z","msg":"非apple用家，見你整得咁色彩繽紛，幫你一推"},{"pid":"af48710f56f18ebf8ed062e8f235718c14d30419","tid":2046550,"uid":356648,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"20b87f6ae15cfa35fa3e8c95343604ac851a1c25","tid":2046550,"uid":49004,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-01T13:11:42.000Z","msg":"都係等第日先download <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-01T13:13:28.000Z","msg":"慢慢唔急<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ebad51ccd0d96ae18396361e71703107b6c08c62","tid":2046550,"uid":356648,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4f436fc1d4557d540facaec754a446c12d30d62d","tid":2046550,"uid":130698,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-01T13:13:21.000Z","msg":"非apple用家，見你整得咁色彩繽紛，幫你一推"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-01T13:13:49.000Z","msg":"多謝<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"168536005d7a2783da6a9ea857fe117b5920d5fa","tid":2046550,"uid":15345,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-01T14:07:46.000Z","msg":"係趕工-&gt;有壓力-&gt;唔想做-&gt;心情差 呢個圈輪迴左好耐<br />\n之後就見到呢個post，依家download黎試下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"h